{"tid":1466832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急勸諫］請以停止機場武鬥捉鬼大會","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:22.000Z","uid":44788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"660083bd7e86d4e02e0a9af869d83d808f3d4fa5","tid":1466832,"uid":44788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:22.000Z","msg":"咁多位大佬 機場係一個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際舞台</span></span>嚟，大家手捉每做一件事都好大機會會上<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各國報章</span></span>。你地係代表緊成個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">運動嘅形象</span></span>，甚至代表全港年青人。記住開機場主線係因為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求同還眼</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n前線請諗清楚<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場唔同衝狗屋</span></span>，請諗清楚捉鬼對機場主線嘅幫助有幾大。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場呢張好牌一定要打得好小心！</span></span><br />\n我地衝禁區，場內打鬥（救少女打狗另計），捉鬼（有機會捉錯）都會係俾機會狗清場而<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全世界都唔可憐</span></span>，相反和理非情況下被清場就<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全世界都屌狗</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油</span></span>啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}